## Get Oriented

Welcome to Outlearn, where we believe in a [better way](https://medium.com/@outlearn/professional-developer-learning-manifesto-afd4f8bf7c96) for developers and dev teams to learn.

You might be here for a bunch of reasons, or you just got seriously lost on the internet.  No matter, this orientation module will give you a quick flavor of what's up with Outlearn so you can make the best of your time here.

**tl;dr**

  - Learn stuff, because you are a learning machine
  - Build paths, share knowledge with your team and the world by curating and writing content in our beautiful path builder tool
  - Author content, using Markdown and GitHub, you can publish your own great training, like a boss

<!-- @section -->

## Learn Stuff

There's a more natural way to learn than classrooms, books, video lectures and conferences.  Visit one of our topic streams.  [How about some love for Node.js](https://www.outlearn.com/topic/nodejs)?

Outlearn learning paths are built out of modules, which might be links to other resources or full-fledged content articles.  For example, check out [this sweet path](https://www.outlearn.com/learn/FaisalAbid/node-path).

