### Innovative Authors Wanted

At Outlearn, we are passionate about enabling the very best possible learning.  We think it starts with taking better advantage of the materials already available.  But there's so much more we can do with the help of innovative authors.

How many tutorials have you read that say 'go write this code, get this result, run this command, get that result'?  You follow along, doing exactly as it tells you, getting exactly the same results, and figuring out nothing on your own!  That kind of content is certainly ubiquitous and easy to write, but way better is the kind that challenges and really gets you thinking.  The best learning presents a problem, forces ideas, tinkering, trial, error, and ultimately a satisfying solution.  

If that resonates with you, [get in touch](mailto:snuggles@outlearn.com).  We're most interested in featuring content that makes great use of creative problem solving, and we've got a lot of ideas in the pipeline to make it easy for you to create that sort of content.

